body:
I'm facing `undefined symbol error for _dataset_ops.so` when I run my compiled tensorflow
both adding it the dependency and protecting it with if static is not showing in source code
despite it was released after

I'm not facing that with the pre-built tensorflow, so, how did this commit slipped from `r1.7`?

https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/releases/tag/v1.7.0
